[3.215582, "o", "\r\n"]
[4.217142, "o", "  Done. Sift is now available inside Claude Code.\r\n\r\n"]
[6.218329, "o", "Step 2: Restart Claude Code - tools appear automatically\r\n\r\n  Claude Code now has 6 new tools:\r\n    - mcp__sift__ingest_report\r\n    - mcp__sift__analyze_results\r\n    - mcp__sift__get_report_stats\r\n    - mcp__sift__get_failure_history\r\n    - mcp__sift__get_flaky_tests\r\n    - mcp__sift__get_severity_trend\r\n\r\n"]
[9.219853, "o", "Step 3: Use it naturally\r\n\r\n  You say: \"Run my tests and analyze the failures with Sift\"\r\n\r\n"]
[11.221103, "o", "  Claude Code will:\r\n    1. Run your test suite (pytest, go test, mvn test, etc.)\r\n    2. Encode the JUnit XML report\r\n    3. Call mcp__sift__ingest_report\r\n    4. Read the structured analysis\r\n    5. Give you actionable suggestions based on root causes\r\n\r\n"]
[14.222626, "o", "--- Example: What Claude Code sees after ingestion ---\r\n\r\n"]
[15.287847, "o", "  Summary: 220/308 tests failed from 3 root causes (12 original, 84 cascading). Categories: 94 infrastructure, 2 assertion. 96 new since last run.\r\n\r\n  Group 1: Docker daemon not available (required by Testcontainers)\r\n           [infrastructure] 56 tests (6 original, 50 cascade)\r\n  Group 2: DataSource not configured: org.springframework.beans.factory.BeanCreationException: Error creating bean with name 'dataSource': Failed to configure a DataSource: 'url'\r\n           [infrastructure] 38 tests (4 original, 34 cascade)\r\n  Group 3: Expected status 404 but was 400\r\n           [assertion] 2 tests (2 original, 0 cascade)\r\n\r\n  Cascade detection: 88% of failures were cascading noise\r\n  Only 12 root failures to investigate (not 220)\r\n"]
[18.293592, "o", "\r\n--- What Claude Code tells you ---\r\n\r\n "]
